EAndreas%20Krieg%2C%20a%20Gulf%20specialist%20at%20the%20Institute%20of%20Middle%20Eastern%20Studies%20at%20King's%20College%20London%2C%20called%20plans%20for%20The%20Line%20%26quot%3Bcompletely%20ludicrous.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Line%20is%20a%20project%20that%20is%20not%20sustainable%3B%20it's%20a%20completely%20ludicrous%20megaproject%20that%20was%20never%20realizable%20because%20of%20the%20sheer%20cost%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20while%20some%20of%20Neom's%20regions%20have%20clear%20aims%2C%20the%20central%20city%20%26quot%3Bhas%20no%20real%20purpose%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bbenefit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20megacity%20is%20also%20set%20to%20include%20an%20octagonal%20floating%20city%20with%20a%20sustainable%20port%2C%20a%20luxury%20island%20resort%2C%20and%20a%20ski%20and%20adventure%20mountain%20range.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20a%20commercial%20statecraft%20strategy%20point%20of%20view%2C%20Neom%20is%20a%20very%20viable%20project%20and%20has%20a%20lot%20going%20for%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Krieg%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20you%20need%20to%20have%20a%20plan%20of%20how%20it%20can%20be%20realized%20to%20attract%20investors%2C%20and%20the%20Saudis%20are%20still%20falling%20short%20of%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228819%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Satellite%20image%20of%20construction%20on%20The%20Line.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6662f8d4cc442a2f676efc5e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225675%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESatellite%20image%20of%20construction%20on%20The%20Line.%3Cp%3ESatellite%20image%20%C2%A92024%20Maxar%20Technologies%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPlans%20for%20the%20megacity%20have%20reportedly%20been%20scaled%20back%20in%20recent%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Line%20was%20originally%20planned%20to%20accommodate%209%20million%20people%20by%202030.%20However%2C%20a