-actor%2C%20Sanjjanaa%20Galrani%2C%20has%20come%20out%20in%20support%20of%20the%20Kannada%20film%20star%2C%20calling%20his%20arrest%20%E2%80%9Cdoomsday%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20industry.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20has%20been%20a%20black%20day%20for%20us%20yesterday%2C%20and%20it's%20been%20like%20a%20doomsday%20for%20the%20Kannada%20industry.%20He%20is%20demigod%20figure%20in%20the%20Kannada%20industry.%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt's%20very%20early%20to%20jump%20the%20gun.%20When%20something%20like%20this%20happens%20with%20a%20celebrity%2C%20if%20there%20is%20a%205%25%20allegation%2C%20it%20becomes%20a%20500%25%20allegation.%20We%20must%20respect%20the%20legal%20process%20and%20not%20jump%20to%20conclusions%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDarshan%20had%20allegedly%20asked%20three%20men%20to%20take%20blame%20for%20the%20crime%20in%20exchange%20of%20cash%2C%20police%20said.%20The%20actor%2C%20who%20was%20arrested%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20offered%20the%20men%20five%20lakh%20rupees%20each%20to%20implicate%20themselves%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718354820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2018-10%2Fpgtnu5lg_divya-spandana-ramya_625x300_03_October_18.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fyou-dont-go-around-killing-people-divya-spandana-on-actor-darshans-arrest-5887640%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Actor-turned-politician%20Divya%20Spandana%20aka%20Ramya%20has%20reacted%20to%20fellow%20Kannada%20actor%20Darshan%20Thoogudeepa's%20arrest%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20murder%20case.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fyou-dont-go-around-killing-people-divya-spandana-on-actor-darshans-arrest-5887640%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fyou-dont-go-around-killing-people-divya-spandana-on-actor-d