20character%20Lieutenant%20Columbo%20in%20the%20TV%20drama%20%26quot%3BColumbo%2C%26quot%3B%20who%20would%20feign%20ignorance%20to%20catch%20people%20off%20guard%20or%20get%20them%20to%20slip%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20leader%2C%20Huang%20is%20incredibly%20hands-on%20and%20meticulous%20in%20his%20attention%20to%20detail%2C%20several%20people%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJensen%20is%20deeply%20involved%20in%20everything%2C%20and%20he%20works%20tirelessly%20%E2%80%94%20I%20think%20work%20is%20his%20hobby%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20current%20employee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20often%20reviews%20slide%20decks%20before%20presentations%20and%2C%20at%20times%2C%20suggests%20last-minute%20changes%20to%20ensure%20they%20meet%20his%20high%20standards%2C%20two%20people%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226339082c-fdbe-440a-829a-b1de4c7f3832%5C%22%3EEmail%20style%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20favors%20a%20flat%20organizational%20structure%2C%20reflected%20in%20Nvidia's%20office%20layout%20in%20the%202000s%2C%20where%20even%20executives%20had%20cubicles.%20That%20was%20a%20way%20to%20avoid%20creating%20separation%20between%20rank-and-file%20staff%20and%20the%20leadership%2C%20a%20former%20senior-level%20employee%20said.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20company's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-jensen-huang-email-style-concise-key-points-insiders-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehouse%20style%20for%20writing%20emails%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20another%20area%20where%20Huang's%20influence%20is%20felt.%20Employees%20are%20expected%20to%20send%20Huang%20and%20their%20department%20a%20list%20of%20their%20top%20five%20priorities%20each%20week.%20Huang%20even%20responds%20to%20some%20of%20these%20emails%2C%20according%20to%20three%20people%2C%20which%20they%20felt%20showed%20his%20engagement%20with%20every%20aspect%20of%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2211caed99-cca4-4ead-9742-9d153454b65a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIntellectual%20h