n%20grilling%26quot%3B%E2%80%94%20intense%20questioning%20by%20Huang.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20people%20BI%20spoke%20to%20said%20they%20had%20felt%20the%20heat%20in%20meetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverybody%20gets%20asked%20tough%20questions%3B%20you're%20expected%20to%20know%20your%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20former%20executive%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20started%20to%20look%20like%20you%20didn't%20know%2C%20he'd%20start%20grilling%20you%20and%20finding%20what%20you%20didn't%20know%20as%20a%20way%20to%20tell%20you%20'go%20get%20on%20top%20of%20this'.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20employee%20likened%20Huang's%20grilling%20to%20an%20attorney's%20interrogation%2C%20noting%20that%20he%20wouldn't%20back%20down%20until%20he'd%20made%20his%20point.%20%26quot%3BSome%20say%20if%20you%20don't%20get%20yelled%20at%20by%20Jensen%2C%20it's%20because%20he%20doesn't%20care%20about%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229f609bb0-e092-4f07-9b2d-f56b444b4acf%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EGenerosity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20is%20also%20known%20inside%20the%20company%20for%20his%20generosity%20and%20philanthropy.%20A%20former%20executive%20said%20he%20has%20opened%20his%20home%20in%20Hawaii%20to%20some%20staff%20and%20even%20made%20them%20breakfast%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-meta-nvidia-jensen-huang-bromance-cooking-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehe%20likes%20to%20cook%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%202010s%2C%20Huang%20decided%20to%20ditch%20company%20Christmas%20parties%20in%20favor%20of%20employees%20doing%20charitable%20work.%20%26quot%3BWe%20started%20helping%20schools%20in%20disrepair%20in%20the%20Bay%20Area%2C%20hiring%20people%20or%20volunteering%20ourselves%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20employee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202011%2C%20when%20Japan%20was%20hit%20by%20an%20earthquake%20and%20tsunami%2C%20Huang%20quickly%20donated%20money%20and%20encouraged%20staff%20to%20do%20t