show%2F110990962.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Review%3A%20Kartik%20Pulls%20Off%20A%20Career-Best%20Performance%20In%20Chandu%20Champion%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20long-forgotten%20but%20incredible%20story%20of%20Murlikant%20Petkar%2C%20India's%20first-ever%20Paralympics%20gold%20medallist%20and%20Padma%20Shri%20recipient%2C%20comes%20alive%20on%20the%20big%20screen%20in%20%3Ci%3EChandu%20Champion%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20a%20sweeping%20and%20somewhat%20overdone%20biopic%20spearheaded%20by%20Kartik%20Aaryan%20as%20the%20spirited%20titular%20hero.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EChandu%20Champion%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20writer-director%20Kabir%20Khan's%20second%20sports%20film%20in%20succession%20(after%2083)%2C%20intense%20emotions%2C%20high%20drama%2C%20anthemic%20music%2C%20athletic%20action%20and%20comic%20interludes%20into%20a%20blender%20to%20capture%20a%20phenomenally%20eventful%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMurlikant's%20life%20was%20one%20that%20witnessed%20more%20twists%20and%20turns%20than%20any%20average%20life%20ever%20does.%20Indeed%2C%20the%20things%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fchandu-champion-screening-kartik-aaryan-with-the-man-himself-murlikant-petkar-5874078%5C%22%3EMurlikant%20Petkar%3C%2Fa%3E%20attempted%20and%20achieved%20as%20a%20young%20man%20was%20indeed%20anything%20but%20commonplace.%20Does%20the%20film%20do%20justice%20to%20him%3F%20Yes%2C%20for%20the%20most%20part.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMurlikant's%20journey%20from%20a%20village%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Sangli%20district%20to%20the%20swimming%20pool%20at%20the%201972%20Summer%20Paralympic%20Games%20in%20Heidelberg%20via%20the%20boxing%20arena%20at%20the%201964%20International%20Military%20Games%20in%20Tokyo%20is%20a%20rousing%20tale%20of%20grit%2C%20determination%20and%20consummate%20self-belief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fkartik-aaryans-cheer-squad-at-chandu-champion-screening-included-vidya-balan-ananya-panday-and-others-5887813%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3EChandu%20Champion%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20might%20have%20worked%20better%20than%20it%20does%20had%20the%20cinematic%20enactment%20been%20a%20touch%20less%20melodramatic%20and%20a%20little%20more%20realistic.%20The%20portrayal%20of%20the%20budding%20wrestler%20of%20Islampur%20and%20his%20exchanges%20with%20his%20friends%2C%20family%20and%20mentors%20are%20frequently%20marred%20by%20emotional%20overreach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20fair%2C%20however%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fkabir-khan-opens-up-on-why-he-cast-kartik-aaryan-as-chandu-champion-5845357%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3EChandu%20Champion%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20pacy%20and%20enjoyable.%20It%20wastes%20no%20time%20in%20hitting%20its%20straps.%20Such%20was%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20life%20that%20it%20brings%20to%20the%20screen%20that%20it%20has%20no%20time%20to%20pause%20for%20breath.%20With%20the%20lead%20actor%20getting%20into%20the%20swing%20of%20things%20with%20all%20his%20might%2C%20the%20exercise%20isn't%20weighed%20down%20as%20other%20such%20films%20are%20by%20the%20cliched%20tropes%20of%20the%20underdog%20drama.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rhythm%20of%20the%20film%20is%20obviously%20dictated%20by%20the%20flow%20of%20Murlikant's%20topsy-turvy%20life.%20It%20flits%20from%20one%20set%20of%20experiences%20to%20another%20as%20the%20protagonist%20encounters%20and%20surmounts%20challenges%20and%20setbacks%20on%20his%20way%20to%20the%20phenomenal%20achievement%20that%20put%20him%20in%20the%20record%20books.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20opening%20moments%20of%20Chandu%20Champion%2C%20a%20wizened%20and%20somewhat%20bitter%20Murlikant%20Petkar%20arrives%20at%20a%20police%20station%20with%20his%20son%20to%20lodge%20a%20formal%20complaint%20against%20the%20President%20of%20India%20for%20not%20giving%20him%20an%20Arjuna%20Award.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FIHQQK_Wn5DM%3Fsi%3DaBp-VbDhbkAOI7Ns%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20skeptical%20SHO%2C%20Inspector%20Sachin%20Kamble%20(Shreyas%20Talpade)%2C%20is%20understandably%20dismissive%20to%20begin%20with%20but%20soon%20gets%20drawn%20into%20Murli's%20account%20of%20his%20dramatic%20ups%20and%20downs.%20The%20flashback%20provides%20the%20film%20its%20narrative%20crux%20while%20rounding%20off%20the%20portrait%20of%20a%20man%20who%20never%20said%20die.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EChandu%20Champion%3C%2Fi%3E%20is%20an%20overtly%20and%20inevitably%20masculine%20film.%20Two%20of%20the%20sports%20that%20it%20showcases%20-%20wrestling%20and%20boxing%20-%20were%20officially%20out%20of%20bounds%20for%20women%20until%20the%20late%201980s%20and%20became%20Olympic%20disciplines%20for%20female%20competitors%20even%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bulk%20of%20the%20film%20plays%20out%20in%20the%201960s%20and%20early%201970s%2C%20when%20women%20were%20never%20anywhere%20near%20the%20wrestling%20or%20boxing%20arena%2C%20let%20alone%20in%20it.%20The%20male%20protagonist%20has%20no%20romantic%20interest%20to%20boot.%20The%20film%2C%20therefore%2C%20has%20no%20room%20for%20love%20ditties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20time%20that%20Murli%20breaks%20into%20song%20and%20dance%20is%20on%20a%20train%20with%20a%20large%20group%20of%20young%20men%20on%20their%20way%20to%20enlist%20in%20the%20Indian%20Army.%20The%20peppy%20musical%20set%20piece%2C%20composed%20by%20Pritam%2C%20gives%20director%20of%20photography%20Sudeep%20Chatterjee%20the%20scope%20to%20pull%20out%20the%20stops%20and%20display%20his%20proven%20virtuosity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20another%20point%2C%20in%20a%20protracted%20and%20crucial%20war%20scene%20filmed%20without%20a%20cut%2C%20the%20cinematographer%20is%20at%20his%20very%20best%20capturing%20the%20rough%20and%20tumble%20of%20battle.%20As%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20film%2C%20editor%20Nitin%20Baid%20imparts%20to%20it%20the%20sort%20of%20pace%20that%20ensures%20that%20Chandu%20Champion%20never%20feels%20overlong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EChandu%20Champion%3C%2Fi%3E%20is%20an%20all-male%20affair.%20Well%2C%20almost.%20The%20film%20has%20three%20secondary%20female%20characters%20-%20Murlikant's%20mother%20(Hemangi%20Kavi)%2C%20an%20Indian%20television%20journalist%20in%20Tokyo%20(Bhagyashri%20Borse)%20and%20another%20present-era%20scribe%20(Sonali%20Kulkarni)%20who%20pulls%20the%20man%20out%20of%20oblivion%20more%20than%20four%20decades%20after%20his%20historic%20Paralympics%20feat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20other%20sports%20dramas%2C%20%3Ci%3EChandu%20Champion%3C%2Fi%3E%20is%20obviously%20not%20limited%20to%20a%20single%20Olympic%20discipline.%20Murlikant%20Petkar%2C%20a%20timid%20and%20bullied%20boy%20who%20fought%20humiliation%20and%20scepticism%20to%20make%20his%20way%20out%20of%20anonymity%2C%20began%20as%20a%20wrestler%2C%20turned%20into%20a%20boxer%20in%20the%20Indian%20Army%20and%20finally%2C%20after%20being%20seriously%20wounded%20in%20the%20Indo-Pak%20war%20of%201965%20and%20paralysed%20from%20the%20waist%20down%2C%20took%20to%2050m%20freestyle%20swimming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20sporting%20arenas%20-%20a%20village%20wrestling%20pit%2C%20a%20Military%20Games%20boxing%20ring%20and%20an%20Olympic%20swimming%20pool%20-%20have%20distinct%20colour%20palettes.%20Each%20necessitates%20a%20specific%20rhythm%20and%20technique.%20That%20helps%20Chandu%20Champion%20keep%20visual%20and%20tonal%20monotony%20at%20bay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMurlikant%2C%20who%20idolised%20freestyle%20wrestler%20Dara%20Singh%2C%20strayed%20into%20wrestling%20because%20he%20believed%20that%20the%20sport%20could%20help%20him%20realise%20his%20dream%20of%20winning%20an%20Olympic%20gold%20medal.%20He%20is%20laughed%20off%20by%20his%20mates%20and%20elders%20but%2C%20as%20life%20takes%20him%20in%20a%20new%20direction%2C%20he%20finds%20men%20who%20see%20his%20potential%20and%20agree%20to%20groom%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20boy%2C%20Murli%20witnesses%20the%20hero's%20welcome%20that%20bronze%20medal-winning%20wrestler%20K.D.%20Jadhav%20receives%20on%20his%20return%20from%20the%201952%20Helsinki%20Olympics.%20The%20sight%20ignites%20in%20him%20a%20desire%20to%20do%20even%20better.%20Murli%20defies%20the%20odds%20and%20finds%20a%20toehold%20in%20the%20village%20wrestling%20akhada%2C%20where%20he%20invites%20trouble%20by%20defeating%20the%20son%20of%20the%20most%20powerful%20man%20in%20the%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latter's%20goons%20chase%20him%20out%20of%20the%20village.%20Murli%20ends%20up%20in%20the%20Army%20and%20becomes%20a%20boxer%20because%20wrestling%20isn't%20a%20defence%20forces%20sport.%20He%20trains%20under%20a%20hard%20taskmaster%2C%20Tiger%20Ali%20(Vijay%20Raaz)%2C%20and%20quickly%20acquires%20exceptional%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20Tiger%20Ali's%20guidance%2C%20Murli%20goes%20from%20being%20%26quot%3BChandu%20Champion%26quot%3B%2C%20a%20disparaging%20sobriquet%20given%20to%20him%20by%20his%20village%20of%20naysayers%20(Chandu%20is%20shorthand%20for%20'loser')%2C%20to%20emerging%20as%20%26quot%3BChhotu%20Tiger%26quot%3B%20-%20as%20his%20boxing%20coach%20christens%20him%20-%20and%20%26quot%3BIndian%20wonder%20boy%26quot%3B%20-%20a%20title%20the%20Japanese%20media%20bestows%20on%20him%20when%20he%20makes%20a%20significant%20mark%20at%20the%201964%20International%20Military%20Games%20in%20Tokyo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%20the%201965%20war%20erupts.%20Murli%20is%20riddled%20with%20nine%20bullets%20but%20survives%20miraculously.%20His%20life%20changes%20in%20more%20ways%20than%20one%20as%20he%20recuperates%20in%20an%20Army%20hospital%2C%20finds%20a%20new%20friend%2C%20Topaz%20(Rajpal%20Yadav)%2C%20in%20the%20medical%20ward%2C%20and%20Tiger%20Ali%20returns%20to%20mentor%20him%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Ficydk-kartik-aaryan-shot-chandu-champion-war-sequence-in-one-take-details-here-5838663%5C%22%3EKartik%20Aaryan%3C%2Fa%3E%20sheds%20his%20free-spirited%20gadabout%20cloak%20and%20gets%20into%20the%20skin%20of%20a%20character%20that%20makes%20a%20slew%20of%20demands%20on%20the%20actor.%20Aaryan%20gives%20the%20physically%20exacting%20role%20all%20he%20has%20and%20pulls%20off%20a%20career-best%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fkartik-aaryans-jaw-dropping-transformation-for-chandu-champion-from-39-body-fat-to-7-5843785%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3EChandu%20Champion%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20one-man%20show%20but%20trust%20Vijay%20Raaz%20to%20turn%20a%20supporting%20role%20into%20something%20much%20more%20than%20that.%20When%20he%20is%20on%20the%20screen%2C%20Kartik%20Aaryan%20has%20to%20concede%20ground%20to%20him.%20But%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20film%20has%20the%20lead%20leading%20from%20the%20front.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EChandu%20Champion%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20which%20celebrates%20an%20unprecedented%20victory%20in%20the%20face%20of%20great%20adversity%2C%20has%20to%20negotiate%20its%20own%20share%20of%20hurdles.%20It%20is%20tripped%20by%20a%20few%20of%20them%20but%20manages%20to%20tide%20over%20the%20rest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EChandu%20Champion%3C%2Fi%3E%20may%20be%20a%20mixed%20bag%20but%20it%20never%20ceases%20to%20be%20uplifting.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718351400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fl01k9bcg_-kartik-aaryan-_625x300_14_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fchandu-champion-review-kartik-aaryan-pulls-off-a-career-best-performance-2-5-stars-5887917%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chandu%20Champion%20Review%3A%20A%20one-man%20show%20but%20trust%20Vijay%20Raaz%20to%20turn%20a%20supporting%20role%20into%2