lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ECelebrating%20the%20success%20with%20Family%20%3F%3F%3F%3F%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FPawankalyan%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Pawankalyan%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FAkiranandan%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Akiranandan%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FqPh0lxFpd6%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FqPh0lxFpd6%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Suresh%20PRO%20(%40SureshPRO_)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSureshPRO_%2Fstatus%2F1797938085814022437%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%204%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20is%20Anna%20Lezhneva%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn1.%20Anna%20Lezhneva%20was%20born%20in%20Russia%20in%201980.%20She%20is%20a%20model-actress%2C%20who%20met%20Pawan%20Kalyan%20during%20the%20filming%20of%20Teen%20Maar%20in%202011.%20Their%20on-set%20romance%20blossomed%20into%20a%20relationship%2C%20and%20after%20two%20years%20of%20dating%2C%20they%20got%20married%20on%20September%2030%2C%202013.%20Ms%20Lezhneva%20is%20Pawan%20Kalyan's%20third%20wife.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn2.%20The%20couple%20has%20a%20son%2C%20Mark%20Shankar%20Pawanovich.%20Ms%20Lezhneva%20also%20has%20a%20daughter%2C%20Polena%20Anjana%20Pawanova%2C%20from%20her%20first%20marriage.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn3.%20Beyond%20her%20modelling%20career%2C%20Ms%20Lezhneva%20is%20rumoured%20to%20own%20hotel%20chains%20in%20Singapore%20and%20is%20said%20to%20have%20assets%2C%20including%20properties%20in%20both%20Russia%20and%20Singapore%2C%20worth%20around%20%E2%82%B91800%20crore.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn4.%20Ms%20Lezhneva's%20relationship%20with%20Mr%20Kalyan%20faced%20scrutiny%20and%20challenges%2C%20given%20the%20Telugu%20superstar's%20marital%20history.%20He%20previously%20married%2019-year-old%20Nandini%20in%201997.%20That%20marriage%20ended%20in%20divorce%20in%202008.%20He%20then%20married%20actress%20Renu%20Desai%20in%202009%2C%20and%20they%20had%20two%20children%2C%20Akira%20Nandan%20and%20Aadhya%2C%20before%20they%20parted%20ways%20in%202012.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn5.%20Reports%20of%20Anna%20Lezhneva%20and%20Pawan%20Kalyan's%20separation%20also%20emerged%20when%20the%20model-actress%20wasn't%20in%20attendance%20at%20important%20family%20gatherings%20such%20as%20Telugu%20star%20Varun%20Tej's%20engagement%20and%20Ram%20Charan%20and%20Upasana's%20daughter's%20cradle%20ceremony.%20However%2C%20despite%20rumours%20of%20marital%20discord%2C%20Ms%20Lezhneva%20has%20been%20actively%20involved%20in%20her%20husband's%20public%20life.%20She%20was%20present%20and%20supportive%20during%20Pawan%20Kalyan's%20recent%20election%20victory%2C%20performing%20traditional%20rituals%20and%20greeting%20fans%2C%20quashing%20separation%20rumours.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718343420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fjh04ufg8_anna-lezhneva-pawan-kalyan_625x300_14_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F5-facts-about-anna-lezhneva-russian-model-and-wife-of-actor-pawan-kalyan-5886973%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Reports%20of%20Anna%20Lezhneva%20and%20Pawan%20Kalyan's%20separation%20also%20emerged%20when%20the%20model-actress%20wasn't%20in%20attendance%20at%20important%20family%20gatherings%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F5-facts-about-anna-lezhneva-russian-model-and-wife-of-actor-pawan-kalyan-5886973%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F5-facts-about-anna-lezhneva-russian-model-and-wife-of-actor-pawan-kalyan-5886973%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F5-facts-about-anna-lezhneva-russian-model-and-wife-of-actor-pawan-kalyan-5886973%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Samsung%20unveils%20Gala