0week%20Rishi%20Sunak%20went%20populist.%20His%20claim%20that%20Labour's%20tax%20plans%20would%20cost%20households%202%2C000%20pounds%20in%20tax%20was%20a%20form%20of%20fake%20news.%20There%20was%20never%20any%20intention%20to%20be%20truthful%20about%20this%20figure%2C%20it%20was%20merely%20a%20device%20for%20forging%20a%20simple%20mental%20association%20between%20the%20words%20%E2%80%9Ctax%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CLabour%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20intended%20to%20mislead%2C%20while%20at%20the%20same%20time%20making%20it%20possible%20for%20Sunak%20to%20deflect%20any%20blame%20onto%20anonymous%20Treasury%20officials%2C%20whom%20he%20claimed%20had%20come%20up%20with%20the%20figures.%20He%20perhaps%20did%20not%20bank%20on%20them%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcd11m307jjvo%5C%22%3Ecalling%20him%20out%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20information%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdl.acm.org%2Fdoi%2Fabs%2F10.1145%2F3309699%3Fcasa_token%3Dlh9-HNBkqX4AAAAA%3ASzjG2Qo-Kwm8VdrAmfwDQY7aTTiFLmFMo9AheS_nRbTTLPI-HHdAr8esP67fQwUPV6YWUB0GgX8%5C%22%3Eweaponised%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20this%20way%2C%20it%20is%20the%20repetition%20of%20the%20argument%2C%20rather%20than%20the%20credibility%20of%20the%20case%2C%20that%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20targeted%20manipulation%20of%20public%20concerns%20on%20specific%20topics.%20%E2%80%9CLabour%20is%20lying.%20Labour%20will%20cost%20you.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20this%20is%20the%20key%20issue.%20Sunak%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyougov.co.uk%2Fpolitics%2Farticles%2F49618-general-election-2024-itv-debate-snap-poll%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cwon%E2%80%9D%20the%20debate%3C%2Fa%3E%20only%20in%20the%20sense%20that%20he%20created%20a%20furore%20that%20revolved%20around%20%E2%80%9CLabour%2Btax%E2%80%9D.%20The%20aim%20was%20never%20to%20tell%20the%20truth%3A%20it%20was%20an%20attempt%20to%20tap%20into%20longstanding%20cultural%20concerns%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%