%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fsgca52qg_pm-modi-in-italy_625x300_14_June_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20time%20when%20a%20Russian%20nuclear%20submarine%20remains%20docked%20in%20Cuba%20merely%2090%20miles%20south%20of%20Florida%2C%20the%20G-7%20leaders%20have%20gathered%20in%20Italy%20for%20the%2050th%20annual%20summit%20of%20the%20grouping%20of%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20richest%20Western%20democracies.%20As%20the%20US-Russia%20tensions%20reach%20nearer%20to%20the%20American%20coast%2C%20Italy's%20Presidency%20of%20the%20G-7%20has%20attempted%20to%20signal%20to%20the%20world%20that%20these%20geopolitical%20contestations%20cannot%20be%20reduced%20to%20a%20'west%20versus%20rest'%20narrative.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Symbolism%20Of%20Apulia%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Italians%20engaged%20in%20symbolism%20by%20hosting%20the%20summit%20in%20Apulia%2C%20a%20region%20in%20the%20southern%20part%20of%20Italy%20that%20is%20historically%20known%20to%20be%20a%20bridge%20between%20Eastern%20and%20Western%20cultures.%20The%20target%20audience%20for%20this%20signalling%20remains%20in%20the%20nations%20from%20the%20broader%20Global%20South%2C%20seen%20as%20non-Western%20states%2C%20as%20the%20G-7%20shows%20that%20it%20is%20ready%20to%20deepen%20collaboration%20with%20developing%20states%20on%20matters%20of%20development%2C%20food%20security%2C%20energy%20security%20and%20climate%20change.%20To%20galvanise%20this%20West-Rest%20collaboration%2C%20Italy%20has%20invited%2015%20guest%20leaders%2C%20of%20which%20six%20are%20members%20of%20the%20G-20%20and%20five%20are%20African%20nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20African%20nations%20attending%20the%20G-7%20remain%20fundamental%20to%20Italy's%20priority%20of%20solving%20the%20problem%20of%20energy%20supplies%20in%20Europe%20by%20connecting%20the%20energy%20transmission%20infrastructure%20of%20Europe%20and%20Africa%20through%20Italy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20six%20guests%20from%20the%20G-20%20include%20India%2C%20Argentina%2C%20Brazil%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20South%20Africa%20and%20Turkey.%20Apart%20from%20Argentina%2C%20where%20there%20is%20a%20substantial%20population%20of%20Italian-origin%20expats%2C%20other%20G-20%20invitees%20hold%20key%20strategic%20and%20security%20implications%20for%20the%20G-7.%20Turkey%20remains%20the%20only%20NATO%20member%20in%20the%20Middle%20East.%20Saudi%20Arabia%20holds%20a%20key%20stake%20in%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict.%20India%2C%20Brazil%20and%20South%20Africa%20fall%20under%20the%20G-7's%20strategic%20calculus%20as%20they%20remain%20key%20representatives%20of%20the%20Global%20South%20and%20are%20either%20recent%20holders%20of%20the%20G-20%20Presidency%20or%20are%20the%20next%20in%20line%20for%20it.%20Rather%20than%20only%20acting%20as%20a%20connecting%20interface%20between%20the%20G-7%20and%20the%20G-20%2C%20these%20three%20nations%20hold%20a%20deeper%20significance%20for%20the%20G-7%20as%20they%20remain%20the%20three%20democratic%20states%20that%20form%20the%20core%20BRICS%20grouping%20along%20the%20adversarial%20Russia%20and%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EVoice%20Of%20The%20Global%20South%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20remains%20central%20to%20the%20G-7's%20calculus%20towards%20the%20Global%20South%20as%20seen%20from%20its%20regular%20presence%20at%20the%20group's%20summits%20as%20a%20guest%20since%202019.%20The%20G-7%20is%20sensitive%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20needs%20the%20global%20south%20giants%20like%20India%20on%20board%2C%20not%20only%20to%20increase%20the%20efficacy%20of%20their%20sanctions%20regime%20on%20Russia%20but%20to%20mechanise%20a%20global%20governance%20architecture%20that%20truly%20bridges%20the%20West%20with%20the%20rest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20rising%20stature%20as%20a%20key%20player%20negotiating%20for%20the%20Global%20South%20while%20upholding%20the%20rules-based%20order%20makes%20it%20a%20natural%20ally%20of%20an%20evolved%20G-7%20that%20places%20its%20policy%20weight%20towards%20being%20more%20egalitarian.%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi's%20visit%20to%20the%20Apulia%20Summit%20gains%20importance%20as%20India%20will%20continue%20to%20voice%20the%20concerns%20of%20the%20developing%20and%20emerging%20economies%20before%20the%20industrialised%20G-7.%20Though%20India's%20stance%20towards%20Russia%20will%20be%20dictated%20by%20its%20own%20strategic%20interests%2C%20PM%20Modi's%20choice%20of%20Apulia%20as%20his%20first%20foreign%20visit%20after%20a%20domestic%20re-election%20signals%20that%20India%20holds%20entrenched%20interests%20in%20its%20partnership%20with%20the%20G-7.%20In%20offering%20policy%20congruence%20towards%20the%20G-7%2C%20India%20complied%20with%20the%20Oil%20Price%20Cap%20on%20Russian%20oil%20while%20strategically%20balancing%20its%20domestic%20oil%20demand.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20key%20area%20of%20friction%20between%20the%20G-7%20and%20India's%20interest%20came%20to%20the%20fore%20in%20the%2012th%20round%20of%20sanctions%20against%20Russia%2C%20when%20the%20G-7%20nations%20imposed%20an%20import%20ban%20on%20Russian-origin%20diamonds%2C%20hurting%20India's%20domestic%20diamond%20export%20industry%20that%20uses%20Russian%20diamonds%20as%20raw%20material.%20It%20is%20expected%20that%20the%20Indian%20presence%20at%20Apulia%20will%20be%20instrumental%20in%20arriving%20at%20a%20common%20understanding%20with%20the%20G-7%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20resolution%20of%20this%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Apulia%20prioritises%20the%20global%20south%2C%20it%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20whether%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20summit%20is%20truly%20beneficial%20for%20the%20developing%20and%20emerging%20economies%20that%20remain%20high%20on%20Italy's%20agenda.%2