at%20could%20benefit%20the%20couple%20immensely.%20On%20her%20advice%2C%20he%20immediately%20left%20for%20Solan%2C%20150%20km%20away%20from%20his%20village%20in%20Kanshipur%2C%20Sirmaur%2C%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20training%2C%20Ranjit%E2%80%99s%20perspective%20on%20farming%20took%20a%20complete%20U-turn.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20decades%2C%20we%20had%20been%20growing%20crops%20using%20chemical%20fertilisers%20like%20urea%2C%20weedicides%2C%20and%20chemical%20insecticides.%20I%20never%20knew%20the%20gravity%20of%20the%20harm%20that%20we%20were%20causing%20ourselves%20and%20to%20those%20buying%20crops%20from%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%2057-year-old%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsidering%20inorganic%20farming%20a%20sin%2C%20the%20couple%20decided%20to%20convert%20their%20entire%20seven-bigha%20(1.4%20acre)%20land%20into%20a%20natural%20farm.%20%E2%80%9CBefore%20training%2C%20I%20thought%20of%20growing%20crops%20on%20a%20small%20part%20of%20our%20land%20using%20natural%20farming%2C%20but%20later%2C%20I%20swore%20never%20to%20use%20any%20chemical%20fertilisers%20in%20the%20field%20again%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fhimachal-2-1717133412.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22With%20zero%20cost%20of%20production%2C%20the%20couple%20has%20doubled%20their%20income%20by%20selling%20vegetables%20and%20fruits.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fhimachal-2-1717133412.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fhimachal-2-1717133412-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fhimachal-2-1717133412-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fhimachal-2-1717133412-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fhimachal-2-1717133412-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-351657%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWith%20zero%20cost%20of%20production%2C%20the%20couple%20has%20doubled%20their%20income%20by%20selling%20vegetables%20and%20fruits.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20month-long%20training%2C%20Ranjit%20returned%20to%20his%20wife%20with%20secret%20tips%20and%20techniques%20of%20natural%20farming.%20Jaswinder%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20knew%20it%20was%20the%20training%20that%20could%20have%20convinced%20her%20husband%20to%20shift%20to%20natural%20farming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%202018%2C%20the%20couple%20has%20been%20cultivating%20at%20least%2025%20kinds%20of%20fruits%2C%20vegetables%2C%20grains%2C%20and%20spices%20including%20lemons%2C%20moringa%2C%20Caprica%20chilies%2C%20pomegranate%2C%20sugarcane%2C%20turmeric%2C%20wheat%2C%20paddy%2C%20guavas%2C%20cauliflower%2C%20spinach%2C%20onions%2C%20beetroot%2C%20ginger%2C%20carrot%2C%20and%20more%20through%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F197256%2Ftelangana-couple-zero-budget-natural-farming-organic-mango-navara-rice-india%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ezero%20budget%20natural%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EZero%20input%20cost%2C%20double%20income%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Jaswinder%20and%20Ranjit%2C%20using%20chemicals%20to%20boost%20production%20from%20the%20field%20was%20the%20only%20way%20to%20farm.%20But%20the%20soil%20kept%20asking%20for%20more.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20noticed%20that%20our%20fertiliser%20usage%20kept%20increasing%20every%20year.%20Initially%2C%20we%20were%20able%20to%20grow%20our%20produce%20using%205-7%20kg%20of%20urea%2C%20however%2C%20we%20were%20later%20forced%20to%20add%2010-12%20kg%20per%20%3Cem%3Ebigha%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlso%2C%20there%20were%20additional%20input%20costs%20for%20recurring%20fertiliser%20and%20pesticide%20usage.%20The%20input%20costs%20for%20us%20were%20Rs%202%2C000%20per%20%3Cem%3Ebigha%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20a%20season.%20Now%2C%20this%20has%20been%20reduced%20to%20zero%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20name%20suggests%2C%20there%20are%20zero%20production%20costs%20in%20zero-budget%20natural%20farming.%20It%20is%20the%20practice%20of%20growing%20crops%20that%20eliminates%20the%20application%20of%20chemical%20inputs%20like%20urea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20advantages%20of%20natural%20farming%2C%20the%20first%20one%20being%20the%20availability%20of%20toxin-free%20food%20and%20rejuvenated%20soil%20health%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jaswinder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fhimachal-3-1717133467.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jaswinder%20and%20Ranjit%20converted%20their%20entire%20seven-bigha%20land%20into%20a%20natural%20farm.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fhimachal-3-1717133467.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fhimachal-3-1717133467-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fhimachal-3-1717133467-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fhimachal-3-1717133467-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fhimachal-3-1717133467-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-351658%5C%22%20height%