t%20how%20food%20is%20grown%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20way%20Mayank%20saw%20it%2C%20he%20was%20faced%20with%20two%20choices%3A%20wallow%20in%20his%20grief%20and%20resort%20to%20unhealthy%20coping%20mechanisms%20or%20channel%20it%20into%20something%20productive.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20no-brainer%20which%20path%20he%20chose%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F270107%2Fterrace-gardening-tips-how-to-grow-vegetables-at-home%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20thriving%20garden%20space%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20%E2%80%98now%20or%20never%E2%80%99%20moment%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20does%20seem%20like%20Mayank%20perfected%20his%20green%20fingers%20in%20no%20time%2C%20he%20argues%20otherwise.%20There%20were%20multiple%20learning%20experiences%2C%20he%20points%20out.%20In%20retrospect%2C%20he%20made%20many%20mistakes%20while%20trying%20to%20get%20his%20plants%20to%20fruit%2C%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTake%20creepers%20like%20bottle%20gourd%20or%20bitter%20gourd%20for%20example.%20What%20I%20have%20now%20understood%20is%20that%20there%20is%20always%20a%20male%20and%20a%20female%20flower%20in%20the%20plant.%20So%2C%20even%20while%20the%20fruit%20is%20being%20borne%20on%20the%20female%20flower%2C%20there%20has%20to%20be%20a%20male%20flower%20for%20pollination%20to%20occur%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-05-22-at-10.13.23-PM_11zon-1716443739-500x879.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mayank%20Sharma%20has%20cultivated%20a%20thriving%20terrace%20garden%20in%20his%20Delhi%