e%2C%20the%20biggest%20concern%20was%20if%20we%20stained%20our%20clothes.%20A%20secret%20code%20%E2%80%98look%E2%80%99%20was%20developed%20and%20passed%20to%20best%20friends%20or%20any%20other%20female%20to%20check%20if%20there%20was%20a%20leakage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20inconvenience%20becomes%20more%20bearable%20with%20age%2C%20the%20horror%20of%20staining%20continues%20for%20most%20of%20our%20lives.%20This%20is%20a%20familiar%20story%20to%20any%20woman%2C%20and%20it%20was%20the%20same%20for%20Ira%20Guha%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Asan%2C%20a%20menstrual%20cup%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20used%20to%20be%20quite%20athletic%20as%20a%20kid%20and%20run%20around.%20I%20loved%20being%20outdoors%20and%20was%20an%20active%20basketball%20player%20in%20my%20school.%20I%20remember%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337583%2Ftulsi-village-chhattisgarh-youtube-village-hummer-studios-being-chhattisgarhiya-alwa-jalwa-gold-cg04%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebeing%20in%20Chhattisgarh%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20a%20state-level%20game%20and%20being%20on%20my%20period.%20There%20were%20no%20bins%20in%20the%20school%2C%20so%20I%20had%20to%20carry%20the%20soiled%20pad%20in%20my%20bag%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares%20with%3Cstrong%3E%20The%20Better%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWalking%20around%20feeling%20disgusted%20and%20embarrassed%20all%20day%20are%20some%20of%20her%20core%20experiences%20that%20shaped%20her%20as%20a%20woman%20in%20the%20menstrual%20hygiene%20business%2C%20she%20says.%20With%20her%20company%20Asan%2C%20she%20has%20helped%20over%2015%2C000%20women%20in%2060%20villages%20in%20Karnataka%20switch%20to%20menstrual%20cups%20so%20far.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20cup%20is%20designed%20to%20make%20periods%20comfortable%20for%20every%20woman.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20rural%20women%2C%20menstrual%20cups%20can%20help%20make%20periods%20easier%20an